<Project Sdk="Microsoft.NET.Sdk">

    <PropertyGroup>
        <GeneratePackageOnBuild>true</GeneratePackageOnBuild>
        <Title>AlastairLundy.Extensions.System</Title>
        <Description>Extensions to C# System classes and structs to help improve them.</Description>
        <Copyright>(c) 2024 Alastair Lundy</Copyright>
        <RepositoryUrl>https://github.com/alastairlundy/SystemExtensions</RepositoryUrl>
        <PackageReleaseNotes>## Changes since 4.2.0

### Additions
* Added Decimal Cuberoot ``Cbrt`` extension method
* Added Double Cuberoot ``Cbrt`` extension method
* Added Decimal Squareroot ``Sqrt`` extension method
* Added Decimal Array ``ToStringArray`` extension method
* Add Squared extensions for Decimal and Double
* Add Cubed extensions for Decimal and Double
* Add extension method to remove Escape Characters from a String

### General Changes
* Replaced equals calls in an extension method
* Removed unnecessary array size parameter
* Replaced equals calls in an extension method
* Replaced English language hardcoding for upper and lower case character detection with language neutral code
* Updated char case detection method

### Deprecations
* Deprecated ``IsCharacterALowerCaseLetter`` extension method - This will be removed in version 5.0 . Please use ``IsLowerCaseCharacter`` method

### Fixed Issues
* XML Doc Comments were missing or incomplete in the Sum class
* XML Doc Comments were missing or incomplete in the HashMap Extensions
* XML Doc Comments were missing or in complete in the Mode class

### Known Issues</PackageReleaseNotes>
